name: orchestration-v2
description: Next-generation pipeline orchestration engine with DAG-based
  parallel execution, FSM lifecycle management, event-sourced SQLite state, and
  CLI-first interface. Use when running multi-phase development pipelines,
  resuming paused workflows, generating pipeline reports, or customizing
  pipeline definitions per-project.
version: 0.1.0
emoji: 🛠️
